-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-05/redecard-shares-valued-at-brl-36-13-to-brl-37-11-correct-.html
(Corrects headline to say BRL 36.13 to BRL 37.11)  Redecard SA (RDCD3)  said NM Rothschild &
Sons Ltda valued its shares at 36.13 reais to 37.11 reais using
a market multiple criteria, the company said in a regulatory
filing today.  Rothschild used  Cielo SA (CIEL3) â€™s stock price to earnings per
share multiple as a model, Redecard said.  Redecard shares were also valued at 34.18 reais to 37.59
reais using the free cash flow to equity method, according to
the filing.  The company hired Rothschild to assess the value of its
shares for an offer made by its controlling shareholder  Itau
Unibanco Holding SA. (ITUB4)   To contact the reporter on this story:
